data.description: 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath, living room, dining area, den, kitchen, breakfast area, big utility room inside, fully fenced in backyard, big lot, workshop, lots of storage!    Air conditioning was replaced in 2014. Heater was replaced in 2021.  Ductwork was replaced in 2020.  Home did not flood.   Gorgeous trees with big back yard for a pool.
